_sText:
This is my first published map.
It's a simple awp/gungame map.
I hope you'll enjoy it as much as my mates and me do.

Feel free to host it on your server, no credits needed as long
as you provide it 'as is' (including 'Read me.txt').

Installation: Unpack and copy/paste it into ...steam/steamapps/youraccountname/counter-strike source/cstrike/maps

Author: -[alpha]- Speedy
Year: 2009.
